-# coding: utf-8
%h2 Stats

%table.table.table-striped.table-hover.table-condensed

  %thead
    %tr
      %th group
      %th name
      %th.text-right value

  %tbody

    - $stats.stats.each do |group, values|

      - values.each do |name, value|
        %tr
          %td= group
          %td= name
          %td.text-right= value

